Barnes hosts a weekly show on his Facebook page called the Weekly Noise. The comedian is heavily involved in the development of the art, hosting weekly open mic sessions at the Obviouzly Armchair in Observatory, where he aims to unearth new talent. The show starts at 9pm and tickets cost R30. He and his colleagues also coach talent and help up-and-coming comedians with their skits. Barnes publishes the Weekly Noise on his Facebook page every Friday. The content will be available here every Sunday.  